{"tid":841804,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"電影 厲害了，我的國 Amazing China 2018年10月4日 香港上映","createTime":"2018-09-29T18:30:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-08T12:38:50.000Z","uid":125193,"like":99,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"ec0cac4d3be6b7f4f4cafd30f14d5aff59915b10","tid":841804,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T18:30:04.000Z","msg":"內容<br />\n電影展現了殲-20、遼寧號航空母艦、港珠澳大橋、中國商飛C919、500米口徑球面無線電望遠鏡、華龍一號、藍鯨2號、神舟十一號、量子科學實驗衛星、復興號電力動車組等場面。內容主要關於習近平總書記自2012年中共十八大上台以來，中國「舉世矚目的成就」，並以「習近平新時代中國特色社會主義思想」作為內在邏輯，彰顯「以習近平同志為核心的黨中央的正確領導」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><br />\n笑而不語</strong></span>           <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/30/023000_7bd938b16d85550f5ca323bcf076e980.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F30%2F023000_7bd938b16d85550f5ca323bcf076e980.jpg&h=5efc79d3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"76eb1d4bf8691a451068b0226b34a9bf29f969de","tid":841804,"uid":82974,"like":35,"dislike":1,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T18:37:03.000Z","msg":"實有中資同奶共老闆送戲飛迫員工睇"},{"pid":"3885483ef3822ae38ab59b747e8856ebeb0aa561","tid":841804,"uid":50740,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T18:39:54.000Z","msg":"有冇得揀返工時間睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4983687076a221e35465189a3ad9c7d792445f5e","tid":841804,"uid":125193,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T18:40:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6gQkdRa6PvQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3